5
00:00:25.339 --> 00:00:26.940
PIS com FIS federal.

6
00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:28.559
Tá certo? Ok.

7
00:00:29.059 --> 00:00:30.480
ICMS e DFAO.

8
00:00:31.399 --> 00:00:33.539
ICMS, incidência, circulação,

9
00:00:33.700 --> 00:00:35.299
vendas interestaduais

10
00:00:35.299 --> 00:00:37.259
para consumidores finais.

11
00:00:37.920 --> 00:00:39.299
O vendedor deve recolher

12
00:00:39.299 --> 00:00:41.259
